WEBVTT

01:42.900 --> 01:46.060
[Love Song in Winter]

01:46.120 --> 01:49.039
[Episode 35]

01:49.200 --> 01:53.450
[Bought a used car in the western suburb]

01:53.509 --> 01:54.390
From when Wen Peng

01:53.570 --> 02:01.290
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

01:54.750 --> 01:56.110
kidnapped Lu Yan until now,

01:56.170 --> 01:57.430
he has changed vehicles

01:57.590 --> 01:59.120
countless times

01:59.150 --> 02:00.770
within Ninghai.

02:01.000 --> 02:02.480
And each change was done

02:03.490 --> 02:04.710
somewhere

02:04.750 --> 02:05.640
outside our surveillance range.

02:06.770 --> 02:08.090
So, he actually has

02:08.120 --> 02:09.440
a chance to leave the city.

02:09.910 --> 02:11.450
But until now,

02:11.660 --> 02:13.550
he's still changing vehicles

02:13.770 --> 02:15.620
in Ninghai.

02:16.420 --> 02:17.690
So I think

02:17.880 --> 02:20.370
he should have a safe house

02:20.870 --> 02:22.940
in Ninghai.

02:22.980 --> 02:23.950
He wants to

02:23.079 --> 02:26.380
[Waited for police to arrive before creating the trap and explosion]

02:23.990 --> 02:25.110
keep changing cars

02:25.110 --> 02:26.640
to lose us

02:26.980 --> 02:28.530
and take Lu Yan

02:28.560 --> 02:30.140
to the safe house.

02:31.079 --> 02:31.770
Captain Jiang,

02:32.190 --> 02:33.390
will the suspect

02:33.390 --> 02:35.100
start hating Lu Yan

02:35.110 --> 02:36.730
and take revenge or hurt her?

02:38.470 --> 02:39.740
It's possible.

02:39.829 --> 02:42.150
But based on the current situation,

02:42.940 --> 02:43.890
I don't think he will.

02:43.850 --> 02:51.160
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

02:43.920 --> 02:45.470
If he wanted to hurt Lu Yan,

02:45.490 --> 02:47.050
he had enough time and opportunities

02:47.079 --> 02:48.960
to do so the first two times

02:50.000 --> 02:51.040
he changed vehicles.

02:51.270 --> 02:52.430
But now it seems

02:53.030 --> 02:53.710
there is no sign

02:53.750 --> 02:55.070
he hurt Lu Yan.

02:55.110 --> 02:56.350
So I think

02:56.900 --> 02:58.470
he still wants to bring Lu Yan

02:58.610 --> 02:59.870
back to the safe house.

03:00.100 --> 03:02.470
Plus, on the photo wall we found

03:02.630 --> 03:03.950
at Wen Peng's house,

03:04.790 --> 03:05.700
other than Lu Yan's photos,

03:05.730 --> 03:06.880
there is a postcard

03:07.970 --> 03:10.450
of Lake Baikal.

03:09.310 --> 03:11.970
[Construction Vehicle] [Old Bay Area] [Nature Preserve]

03:10.810 --> 03:12.550
On the back, it says,

03:12.790 --> 03:13.350
"Lu Yan,

03:13.570 --> 03:14.790
do you want to

03:14.830 --> 03:16.360
go to Lake Baikal with me?"

03:16.710 --> 03:18.270
I think with Wen Peng's personality

03:18.300 --> 03:19.310
and behavior,

03:19.710 --> 03:21.900
he should have

03:22.150 --> 03:24.790
a lakeside safe house within Ninghai.

03:25.260 --> 03:27.670
He's taking Lu Yan there now.

03:29.640 --> 03:30.550
So the main focus

03:30.550 --> 03:31.190
of our search now

03:31.770 --> 03:34.610
is all the lakes within

03:34.990 --> 03:36.470
and around Ninghai,

03:36.870 --> 03:38.920
as long as they meet two points.

03:38.950 --> 03:39.640
One,

03:39.940 --> 03:40.880
people can live there.

03:41.270 --> 03:41.900
Two,

03:42.310 --> 03:43.400
it's not easy to be found.

03:43.490 --> 03:45.000
We need to check all of them.

03:45.630 --> 03:45.990
Understood.

03:46.010 --> 03:46.720
-Yes.
-Yes, sir.

03:46.740 --> 03:47.329
Understood.

03:55.800 --> 03:58.040
[Map of Ninghai City]

04:18.240 --> 04:19.050
You're awake.

04:21.610 --> 04:22.950
Did you sleep well last night?

04:27.120 --> 04:28.140
What do you want to eat?

04:29.630 --> 04:30.980
I remember you like noodles.

04:32.720 --> 04:34.000
I can't go on like this.

04:34.570 --> 04:35.659
I have to find a way.

04:36.570 --> 04:37.610
I'll make it for you.

04:38.560 --> 04:39.659
I want to go to the toilet.

04:48.030 --> 04:48.590
Sure.

05:04.890 --> 05:06.590
Menthol can make the nervous system

05:05.940 --> 05:08.710
[Baking Soda] [Bamboo Charcoal Mint]

05:06.590 --> 05:07.640
feel cold

05:07.950 --> 05:09.420
and make the body heat up against it.

05:31.600 --> 05:32.520
What's wrong?

05:33.790 --> 05:35.200
Are you okay?

05:37.130 --> 05:38.180
I'm fine.

05:48.560 --> 05:50.850
Hurry up and get a fever.

06:08.600 --> 06:09.220
Lu Yan?

06:24.830 --> 06:25.670
Are you okay?

06:26.330 --> 06:27.620
Let me help you. Slowly.

06:35.290 --> 06:36.210
Are you okay?

06:38.270 --> 06:39.140
Are you okay?

06:40.200 --> 06:40.970
What's wrong?

06:48.240 --> 06:49.290
Do you have a fever?

06:50.360 --> 06:51.000
Here.

06:51.210 --> 06:52.940
Let me help you sit over there.

06:56.760 --> 06:57.159
Come.

06:57.820 --> 06:58.400
Here.

07:30.630 --> 07:31.780
Wait here for a while.

07:31.810 --> 07:32.790
I'll buy you some medicine.

08:14.580 --> 08:17.240
[Office of Criminal Investigation Unit]

08:17.160 --> 08:17.990
There are 14 lakes

08:18.030 --> 08:19.480
in Ninghai City.

08:19.630 --> 08:21.830
Other than the seven artificial lakes in the city,

08:21.850 --> 08:23.840
most of the remaining ones are around

08:23.950 --> 08:25.600
the Bay Area and Puxi District.

08:25.750 --> 08:26.670
According to our investigation,

08:26.690 --> 08:27.520
there are three places

08:27.630 --> 08:28.310
that are sparsely populated,

08:28.750 --> 08:29.750
inhabitable,

08:29.800 --> 08:30.630
and close to the lake.

08:30.950 --> 08:31.950
The first one is Fairy Lake.

08:32.070 --> 08:33.270
Only the textile factory and

08:33.480 --> 08:34.320
employee dorms from before

08:34.320 --> 08:35.909
remain around it now.

08:36.390 --> 08:37.500
The second is Gaoyang Lake.

08:37.669 --> 08:38.470
It's also the biggest lake

08:38.470 --> 08:39.299
in Ninghai City.

08:39.630 --> 08:41.350
There are empty abandoned buildings

08:41.549 --> 08:42.400
and a villa area around it.

08:43.030 --> 08:44.530
The third is Longmen Lake.

08:44.670 --> 08:46.110
Near it is the most famous

08:46.150 --> 08:47.300
commercial street from before,

08:47.320 --> 08:48.420
but it has been abandoned.

08:49.110 --> 08:50.310
The above three lakes

08:50.390 --> 08:51.350
are the most likely places

08:51.390 --> 08:52.470
where the suspect is hiding.

08:57.400 --> 08:58.660
These three places

08:59.150 --> 09:00.260
are far away.

09:00.470 --> 09:01.070
How about this?

09:01.780 --> 09:03.220
Divide into three teams

09:03.720 --> 09:04.470
and check them one by one.

09:05.200 --> 09:06.190
Search thoroughly.

09:06.310 --> 09:07.020
-Yes.
-Yes, sir.

10:28.350 --> 10:29.730
The door has been unlocked.

10:42.730 --> 10:43.480
Lu Yan.

10:45.350 --> 10:46.080
Lu Yan.

10:48.840 --> 10:49.620
Lu Yan?

10:51.640 --> 10:52.370
Lu Yan!

11:08.340 --> 11:10.490
Help! Is anyone there?

11:10.590 --> 11:11.650
Help!

11:43.630 --> 11:44.630
Meng,

11:45.460 --> 11:47.370
do you think we can catch fish here?

11:49.150 --> 11:50.410
I doubt it here.

11:52.470 --> 11:54.230
There must be fish

11:54.230 --> 11:55.110
where we were yesterday.

11:56.380 --> 11:57.910
It was those people who set off fireworks

11:57.950 --> 11:59.070
that ruined it.

11:59.630 --> 12:00.990
Aren't fireworks not allowed here?

12:02.740 --> 12:04.090
Horrible,

12:04.100 --> 12:04.880
these people.

12:05.310 --> 12:06.720
I don't know where they came from.

12:06.740 --> 12:07.440
Sirs,

12:07.920 --> 12:08.910
yesterday,

12:08.950 --> 12:10.080
someone set off fireworks here?

12:10.260 --> 12:11.370
Exactly.

12:11.590 --> 12:13.240
Someone set off fireworks here yesterday.

12:13.630 --> 12:14.430
Where?

12:14.470 --> 12:15.070
Which direction?

12:16.330 --> 12:17.660
Across the lake,

12:18.190 --> 12:19.670
about five kilometers away.

12:20.760 --> 12:21.690
Over there, right?

12:21.790 --> 12:22.640
Yes.

12:23.580 --> 12:25.080
Okay, thank you.

12:52.560 --> 12:54.060
Why did you do that?

12:54.990 --> 12:56.680
You like killing, don't you?

12:58.430 --> 12:59.510
Kill me too.

13:00.220 --> 13:01.590
I've been so good to you.

13:01.950 --> 13:03.310
I've been giving you chances.

13:04.320 --> 13:04.900
Weren't we

13:04.900 --> 13:05.910
just fine yesterday?

13:05.930 --> 13:07.150
Why did you hurt me?

13:08.750 --> 13:09.790
You let me down.

13:12.030 --> 13:13.670
You're crazy.

13:16.540 --> 13:17.900
Even if you kill me,

13:19.200 --> 13:20.350
I won't be with you.

13:26.690 --> 13:28.110
Is it because of Jiang Chengyi?

13:34.710 --> 13:36.970
Jiang Chengyi, Jiang Chengyi, Jiang Chengyi!

13:37.000 --> 13:38.110
Jiang Chengyi!

13:38.950 --> 13:40.670
Why is it always Jiang Chengyi?

13:40.980 --> 13:42.070
Why do you all love him

13:42.070 --> 13:43.410
instead of me?

13:43.910 --> 13:45.790
He took everything from me.

13:45.810 --> 13:46.550
He stole

13:46.550 --> 13:47.700
everything from me!

13:47.830 --> 13:48.430
He forced me

13:48.450 --> 13:49.640
to this point!

13:49.670 --> 13:50.850
Why?

13:52.790 --> 13:53.870
I'll kill him now.

13:53.900 --> 13:55.480
You chose all of this.

13:57.200 --> 13:59.390
No one stole your things.

14:00.410 --> 14:02.090
You don't love me either.

14:02.280 --> 14:04.440
You just want to defeat Jiang Chengyi.

14:04.920 --> 14:06.060
From beginning to end,

14:06.290 --> 14:07.720
you only hate yourself.

14:07.750 --> 14:09.130
Shut up! What do you know?

14:11.000 --> 14:12.030
You kill people

14:12.070 --> 14:13.790
to make up for your fear

14:14.040 --> 14:15.520
and your childhood trauma.

14:15.540 --> 14:17.030
Wen Peng, don't be silly.

14:17.070 --> 14:17.740
Do you think doing this

14:17.760 --> 14:19.430
will make someone love you?

14:39.610 --> 14:40.870
In that case,

14:41.030 --> 14:42.320
let me tell you.

14:46.550 --> 14:47.330
Deng Man...

14:50.120 --> 14:51.280
was also killed by me.

14:57.360 --> 14:58.260
Jiang Chengyi!

14:58.330 --> 14:59.530
Happy birthday.

14:59.680 --> 15:00.490
Thank you.

15:00.660 --> 15:01.750
I knitted it myself.

15:01.760 --> 15:02.530
Look.

15:02.550 --> 15:03.970
It's my first time doing such a thing.

15:04.280 --> 15:05.330
Give me a chance.

15:05.360 --> 15:06.220
I like you.

15:06.240 --> 15:07.910
I really like you!

15:29.990 --> 15:31.200
It's you?

15:31.250 --> 15:32.360
What's up?

15:32.380 --> 15:33.760
Why are you so mysterious?

15:35.060 --> 15:36.870
You dared to come without knowing who it was?

15:37.450 --> 15:38.740
You're quite brave.

15:39.270 --> 15:40.430
Cut the crap.

15:40.830 --> 15:41.800
Just say it.

15:49.880 --> 15:50.840
What?

16:05.090 --> 16:06.330
How much do you want?

16:09.240 --> 16:10.120
I'm giving it for free.

16:11.020 --> 16:12.810
Do whatever you want.

16:12.980 --> 16:14.130
For free?

16:14.480 --> 16:15.870
Are you that kind?

16:16.830 --> 16:17.650
Why?

16:23.190 --> 16:24.110
Because

16:25.790 --> 16:26.950
we have the same goal.

16:34.090 --> 16:34.790
Fine.

16:35.230 --> 16:36.490
Wait for my good news.

17:15.660 --> 17:16.550
You...

17:16.569 --> 17:18.310
Don't take it too hard.

17:24.089 --> 17:25.980
I really have no choice.

17:26.010 --> 17:28.420
I don't want to hurt anyone.

17:30.800 --> 17:31.870
How could Ding Jing

17:31.910 --> 17:32.790
do such a thing?

17:36.750 --> 17:38.150
I can't let Coach Zhou

17:38.170 --> 17:39.220
lose his reputation.

17:40.720 --> 17:42.480
What should I do?

17:44.510 --> 17:46.190
What should I do?

17:46.930 --> 17:47.430
Wen,

17:47.430 --> 17:48.840
do you have any ideas?

17:51.560 --> 17:52.600
I have an idea.

17:54.570 --> 17:56.050
We can put on a show

17:56.590 --> 17:57.840
to scare Ding Jing.

18:04.550 --> 18:05.740
Have you made up your mind?

18:11.460 --> 18:12.440
Yes.

18:12.920 --> 18:14.090
You're right.

18:14.820 --> 18:16.650
As long as Ding Jing thinks I'm dead,

18:17.130 --> 18:18.410
she will be scared.

18:18.430 --> 18:19.830
She won't dare to do anything again.

18:23.380 --> 18:25.430
But I still hurt Lu Yan.

18:26.920 --> 18:27.810
It's okay.

18:28.320 --> 18:29.640
When everything is over,

18:29.890 --> 18:30.430
you can

18:30.470 --> 18:31.430
explain it to her.

18:32.600 --> 18:33.700
Wen.

18:34.360 --> 18:37.400
If Lu Yan thinks

18:37.420 --> 18:38.470
I'm really dead,

18:38.510 --> 18:39.400
will she think

18:39.400 --> 18:40.550
she forced me to die?

18:41.130 --> 18:41.740
No.

18:41.860 --> 18:43.180
I will always be with her.

18:43.420 --> 18:44.700
When the time is right,

18:44.780 --> 18:46.640
I'll tell her the truth.

18:46.900 --> 18:48.650
When the time is right?

18:50.040 --> 18:51.750
If Lu Yan and Tang Jie

18:51.790 --> 18:52.750
know in advance,

18:52.770 --> 18:53.990
we'll definitely be exposed.

18:54.230 --> 18:55.040
So,

18:55.270 --> 18:57.180
we have to fool everyone

18:57.560 --> 18:58.700
before we can fool Ding Jing.

19:02.190 --> 19:03.070
I see.

19:05.390 --> 19:06.970
After the video recording,

19:07.400 --> 19:09.290
go hide in a hotel for a few days.

19:09.650 --> 19:11.240
I'll give the video to Ding Jing

19:11.520 --> 19:12.450
and tell her

19:12.830 --> 19:14.200
she forced you to die.

19:14.350 --> 19:15.190
I'll make her

19:15.230 --> 19:16.700
hand over the video of you and Coach Zhou.

19:17.190 --> 19:18.640
If she doesn't,

19:18.830 --> 19:20.100
I'll tell the police.

19:20.130 --> 19:21.020
Wen,

19:21.270 --> 19:22.570
I'll leave the rest

19:22.600 --> 19:23.850
to you then.

19:23.880 --> 19:25.850
Please take care of Lu Yan for me.

19:25.910 --> 19:27.420
She must not have anything happen to her.

19:28.460 --> 19:29.380
Don't worry.

19:31.550 --> 19:32.590
Is the will ready?

19:33.670 --> 19:34.730
It's in my bag.

19:35.620 --> 19:36.990
Per your instructions,

19:37.150 --> 19:38.640
I didn't write Ding Jing's name.

19:38.740 --> 19:40.150
The content is vague too.

19:42.490 --> 19:43.530
Otherwise,

19:43.550 --> 19:45.320
if the police see the suicide note,

19:45.510 --> 19:47.030
they'll go to Ding Jing first.

19:47.150 --> 19:48.390
Then the video will be wasted.

19:50.030 --> 19:50.790
Wen,

19:50.900 --> 19:52.230
you're really thoughtful.

19:52.650 --> 19:54.510
Thank you for doing so much for me.

19:56.340 --> 19:57.420
Are you ready?

20:00.420 --> 20:01.310
Yes.

20:02.270 --> 20:03.210
Let's start.

20:17.060 --> 20:17.970
Ding Jing.

20:19.040 --> 20:20.950
I'm desperate because of you.

20:22.760 --> 20:24.480
I won't let you have your way.

20:26.270 --> 20:27.940
Since you're forcing me,

20:28.330 --> 20:29.850
I'll kill myself.

20:31.710 --> 20:33.670
I want you to remember your entire life

20:33.710 --> 20:35.310
that I died

20:35.620 --> 20:37.570
because of you!

21:42.070 --> 21:42.790
Deng Man.

21:43.400 --> 21:44.200
Deng Man.

21:50.130 --> 21:50.970
Wen!

21:51.750 --> 21:52.630
Is it enough?

21:54.500 --> 21:56.050
Yes, it's enough.

21:56.430 --> 21:57.400
Come up now.

22:06.440 --> 22:07.220
Help me!

22:09.950 --> 22:11.230
Deng Man, grab the branch!

22:11.270 --> 22:12.360
Hurry, grab the branch!

22:17.400 --> 22:18.300
Help me!

22:26.630 --> 22:28.120
If you really die,

22:28.680 --> 22:30.390
Lu Yan and Jiang Chengyi...

22:33.310 --> 22:34.400
Wen, help me!

22:43.620 --> 22:44.540
Help me!

23:45.880 --> 23:48.080
[So I'm destined not to get the person I want, right?]

23:45.880 --> 23:48.080
[God seems to enjoy torturing me.]
[My looks are average, my family is average, my education is average.]

24:04.110 --> 24:05.560
I will never forget

24:06.850 --> 24:08.580
how she struggled in the lake.

24:11.250 --> 24:12.850
She wanted me to save her.

24:14.870 --> 24:15.890
But I didn't.

24:19.430 --> 24:20.750
I just watched as she

24:22.100 --> 24:23.120
slowly

24:25.150 --> 24:27.000
sank to the bottom of the lake.

24:40.080 --> 24:41.350
Why don't you go die?

24:43.480 --> 24:44.710
You should die.

24:44.920 --> 24:46.610
Why don't you go die?

24:47.390 --> 24:49.490
Go to hell!

24:56.580 --> 24:57.900
I will die.

25:01.040 --> 25:02.390
But I want Jiang Chengyi

25:02.430 --> 25:03.470
to personally see

25:05.110 --> 25:07.560
you and I

25:09.180 --> 25:10.470
die together.

25:25.750 --> 25:26.750
Wen.

25:27.200 --> 25:28.150
I'm here to see Lu Yan

25:28.190 --> 25:29.510
on behalf of the school.

25:30.660 --> 25:31.630
Is she okay?

25:31.870 --> 25:33.250
She still has a fever.

25:33.270 --> 25:34.790
It's been two days.

25:34.820 --> 25:36.400
We'll have to go to a big hospital if she doesn't recover.

25:40.200 --> 25:41.280
Wen,

25:41.310 --> 25:43.070
can you do me a favor?

25:43.390 --> 25:44.830
Lu Yan and I still have a thesis

25:44.870 --> 25:45.980
that we haven't submitted.

25:46.050 --> 25:47.630
I need to get it done.

25:47.870 --> 25:49.720
Can you take care of her for me?

25:50.180 --> 25:51.250
Sure, no problem.

25:51.610 --> 25:52.690
Thank you, Wen.

25:53.280 --> 25:54.630
Call me if you need anything.

25:54.670 --> 25:55.470
I'll be back soon.

25:55.490 --> 25:55.950
Okay.

26:32.880 --> 26:34.500
[I'm leaving today. Can we meet for the last time? I'll wait for you at the sports field.]

27:18.860 --> 27:20.580
I'm leaving today.

27:20.460 --> 27:21.660
[Copy] [Forward] [Delete]

27:21.030 --> 27:22.500
Can we meet for the last time?

27:21.790 --> 27:24.110
[Cancel] [Delete]

27:21.790 --> 27:24.110
[Confirm Deletion]

27:23.180 --> 27:24.370
I'll wait for you at the sports field.

27:49.950 --> 27:50.620
[Reject] [Answer]

27:49.950 --> 27:50.620
[Jiang Chengyi]

27:56.610 --> 27:58.500
[The other party has rejected the call]

27:56.610 --> 27:58.500
[I'm leaving today. Can we meet for the last time? I'll wait for you at the sports field.]

28:07.130 --> 28:13.270
[Lu Yan, you're so cruel. I'm leaving. We will never meet again.]

28:18.340 --> 28:21.690
[Lu Yan, you're so cruel. I'm leaving. We will never meet again.]

28:24.260 --> 28:25.180
[Copy] [Forward] [Delete]

28:25.270 --> 28:26.100
[Cancel] [Delete]

28:25.270 --> 28:26.100
[Confirm Deletion]

28:27.420 --> 28:28.020
[Reminder] [Delete]

28:28.050 --> 28:28.640
[Cancel] [Delete]

28:28.050 --> 28:28.640
[Confirm Deletion]

29:31.770 --> 29:32.280
Hello.

29:33.950 --> 29:34.750
Captain Jiang,

29:35.410 --> 29:36.760
you finally found me.

29:38.320 --> 29:39.290
Keep walking.

29:40.450 --> 29:41.380
I'm right outside.

29:56.070 --> 29:58.330
[Lehu Villa]

29:59.810 --> 30:00.670
Attention, everyone.

30:00.690 --> 30:02.050
The suspect kidnapped the hostage.

30:02.070 --> 30:03.780
They're in the Lehu Villa area 15 kilometers away

30:03.810 --> 30:04.630
from Gaoyang Lake.

30:04.640 --> 30:05.320
Roger.

30:09.370 --> 30:10.270
Command Center,

30:10.300 --> 30:11.060
I request for the SWAT Team

30:11.080 --> 30:12.030
and snipers to be in position.

30:12.060 --> 30:13.300
Roger.

30:35.840 --> 30:36.740
Captain Jiang,

30:38.050 --> 30:39.770
what do you think of the scenery here?

30:41.530 --> 30:42.850
It's beautiful!

30:45.380 --> 30:46.660
It's very suitable

30:47.210 --> 30:49.110
for us two to live together.

31:00.490 --> 31:01.620
In the end,

31:02.530 --> 31:03.710
you still lost.

31:05.040 --> 31:06.010
Wen Peng,

31:08.270 --> 31:09.750
why must you do this?

31:10.080 --> 31:11.100
I'm here today

31:11.270 --> 31:12.230
to tell you that...

31:12.250 --> 31:13.550
Alright, Captain Jiang.

31:14.320 --> 31:15.690
I know what you want to say.

31:16.310 --> 31:17.640
You just want to

31:17.670 --> 31:18.860
replace Lu Yan

31:18.880 --> 31:20.230
and be the hostage, right?

31:25.000 --> 31:27.550
Captain Jiang is so brave.

31:29.020 --> 31:29.670
Are you doing this

31:29.690 --> 31:31.220
to highlight

31:32.020 --> 31:33.590
your great and selfless

31:33.620 --> 31:34.700
sacrifice for love?

31:36.660 --> 31:38.030
Captain Jiang, listen.

31:38.600 --> 31:40.240
You will never get Lu Yan.

31:42.180 --> 31:43.390
She is mine.

31:49.480 --> 31:50.980
Since you're here today,

31:51.240 --> 31:52.640
I want to tell you that

31:53.720 --> 31:55.360
we are going to be together.

31:58.750 --> 31:59.430
And you

32:00.820 --> 32:03.180
will live in guilt

32:03.660 --> 32:04.820
and pain forever.

32:09.560 --> 32:10.470
Wen Peng,

32:12.280 --> 32:13.530
you're wrong.

32:14.740 --> 32:15.690
I'm here

32:17.390 --> 32:18.430
to see

32:18.430 --> 32:20.340
how cowardly

32:20.740 --> 32:22.220
and despicable you are.

32:24.290 --> 32:25.740
You put in so much effort

32:25.770 --> 32:27.120
for me to find this place

32:28.280 --> 32:29.150
just for me to see

32:29.150 --> 32:30.470
you two die here?

32:34.900 --> 32:36.390
You've done so many things

32:37.280 --> 32:38.690
and killed so many people.

32:39.090 --> 32:40.770
Isn't your final goal

32:41.940 --> 32:43.190
just to stop Lu Yan

32:43.190 --> 32:44.270
from being with me?

32:44.990 --> 32:46.350
Then you messed up.

32:46.890 --> 32:48.900
Since you have the guts to kill,

32:49.690 --> 32:50.950
then why don't you

32:50.990 --> 32:51.710
just kill me?

32:53.590 --> 32:54.810
Why won't you kill me?

32:56.680 --> 32:57.590
You're a coward

32:58.460 --> 32:59.480
and don't dare, right?

33:01.750 --> 33:03.300
Even today, you have to

33:03.300 --> 33:03.870
hide behind a woman

33:03.870 --> 33:05.290
to face me.

33:06.990 --> 33:07.820
Wen Peng,

33:08.220 --> 33:09.720
I'll give you a chance today.

33:10.900 --> 33:12.110
I'll let you

33:13.050 --> 33:14.840
be a true man.

33:16.190 --> 33:17.370
What do you mean?

33:22.370 --> 33:23.570
Take it.

33:23.620 --> 33:24.420
Kill me.

33:26.190 --> 33:27.110
And everything will be settled.

33:34.400 --> 33:35.400
Pick it up.

33:35.890 --> 33:36.950
You think I'm a kid?

33:38.370 --> 33:39.930
Do you think I'm a three-year-old?

33:40.910 --> 33:42.000
After killing me,

33:42.570 --> 33:43.910
Lu Yan can no longer

33:43.910 --> 33:44.750
be with me.

33:45.760 --> 33:46.510
Your mom

33:46.540 --> 33:48.240
can go home and keep loving you.

33:49.130 --> 33:49.840
Right?

33:50.700 --> 33:51.900
Everyone will be happy.

33:52.210 --> 33:53.460
Everything will be solved.

33:53.550 --> 33:54.470
Everything you lost

33:54.510 --> 33:55.440
will come back to you.

34:31.600 --> 34:32.540
Attention, sniper.

34:32.570 --> 34:34.239
The suspect is too close to the hostage

34:34.310 --> 34:35.560
and they're connected by a rope.

34:35.580 --> 34:36.500
Don't shoot for now.

34:36.530 --> 34:37.429
Wait for the best timing.

34:37.460 --> 34:37.929
Got it.

34:46.040 --> 34:46.780
Wen Peng.

34:47.750 --> 34:49.030
I was right about you.

34:49.920 --> 34:52.409
You are a cowardly,

34:53.230 --> 34:54.030
self-abased,

34:54.870 --> 34:56.210
and unaccomplished person.

34:56.830 --> 34:58.070
This is the chance.

34:59.250 --> 35:00.870
Take back everything you lost.

35:02.300 --> 35:03.020
Do it.

35:07.370 --> 35:08.830
Pick it up.

35:11.960 --> 35:13.250
Don't you hate me?

35:13.510 --> 35:14.530
I'll give you a chance.

35:14.830 --> 35:15.350
Kill me.

36:04.380 --> 36:05.360
Are you okay?

36:35.130 --> 36:36.450
I wanted to die.

36:39.740 --> 36:41.160
But I wanted Jiang Chengyi

36:41.200 --> 36:42.370
to personally see

36:43.930 --> 36:46.270
you and I

36:47.930 --> 36:49.200
die together.

36:52.480 --> 36:55.020
[Three months later]

36:56.890 --> 36:58.880
I'm watching my mom.

36:59.180 --> 36:59.980
I...

37:00.580 --> 37:01.760
Wait for a while.

37:02.010 --> 37:03.370
I'll give you the proposal.

37:06.870 --> 37:07.390
Okay.

37:16.530 --> 37:17.210
Okay.

37:18.590 --> 37:19.860
Yan.

37:23.260 --> 37:24.130
Mom!

37:25.620 --> 37:26.340
Mom.

37:27.190 --> 37:28.030
Mom.

37:29.000 --> 37:30.640
I'm here.

37:30.720 --> 37:31.710
What's wrong?

37:32.280 --> 37:34.050
Where am I?

37:35.380 --> 37:35.910
You...

37:36.430 --> 37:37.810
You're in the hospital.

37:38.270 --> 37:39.420
How are you?

37:39.870 --> 37:40.630
Mom.

37:42.230 --> 37:43.070
Hurts.

37:43.710 --> 37:44.350
It hurts?

37:45.510 --> 37:46.720
I'll call the doctor.

37:46.880 --> 37:48.190
Yan.

37:50.460 --> 37:51.220
What is it?

37:52.130 --> 37:52.880
Is...

37:52.910 --> 37:55.310
Is Jiang okay?

38:00.310 --> 38:01.690
Jiang is fine.

38:02.630 --> 38:03.820
He

38:04.340 --> 38:05.490
will come to see you soon.

38:08.030 --> 38:09.110
Don't cry.

38:09.150 --> 38:10.430
Don't cry.

38:11.370 --> 38:12.560
You scared me.

38:14.330 --> 38:15.260
Alright, Mom.

38:25.120 --> 38:25.900
Comrades,

38:26.390 --> 38:27.530
faced with this complicated

38:27.850 --> 38:30.520
and arduous case

38:30.680 --> 38:32.650
during this time,

38:33.190 --> 38:34.900
you all took the initiative

38:35.160 --> 38:36.250
and challenge.

38:36.280 --> 38:37.740
You expanded the investigation

38:37.760 --> 38:40.220
and searched for clues day and night,

38:40.240 --> 38:41.400
cooperating closely

38:42.070 --> 38:43.310
and showing

38:43.350 --> 38:44.680
our professionalism

38:44.700 --> 38:46.060
and teamwork.

38:46.900 --> 38:48.130
You have cracked

38:48.400 --> 38:50.410
the biggest serial murder case

38:50.640 --> 38:51.990
in the city's history

38:52.470 --> 38:54.590
and investigated the unsolved case from eight years ago.

38:54.640 --> 38:56.180
You successfully brought the criminal

38:56.210 --> 38:57.080
to justice.

38:58.820 --> 39:00.850
Given your excellent performance,

39:00.870 --> 39:02.130
the Provincial Public Security Bureau

39:02.630 --> 39:03.960
gave our battalion

39:04.570 --> 39:05.800
a collective third-class merit.

39:06.050 --> 39:07.520
On behalf of the Party Committee,

39:07.760 --> 39:10.670
I sincerely congratulate you all.

39:11.040 --> 39:12.260
I hope you all

39:12.450 --> 39:14.090
will continue

39:14.280 --> 39:15.480
improving

39:15.680 --> 39:16.860
and making good results

39:17.070 --> 39:18.200
in your future work.

39:28.820 --> 39:30.310
It's good.

39:30.560 --> 39:32.270
It's okay.

39:32.290 --> 39:32.880
Liu Hao.

39:33.580 --> 39:34.590
Lei Yiming could've

39:34.590 --> 39:35.470
hung it by reaching out.

39:35.470 --> 39:36.760
Why are you standing there?

39:37.050 --> 39:38.850
Can't you see me?

39:40.860 --> 39:42.330
You all really forgot me.

39:42.360 --> 39:43.440
No.

39:43.500 --> 39:45.030
Why did you leave the hospital

39:45.060 --> 39:45.800
instead of resting a bit more?

39:45.830 --> 39:46.750
I heard that you guys

39:46.790 --> 39:47.670
are asking for a beating.

39:47.690 --> 39:48.820
Captain Jiang can't do it,

39:48.850 --> 39:49.490
so I came out

39:49.510 --> 39:50.310
to teach you all a lesson.

39:50.220 --> 39:52.250
[Collective Third-Class Merit]

39:50.720 --> 39:52.180
We really missed you.

39:52.400 --> 39:52.950
For what?

39:52.970 --> 39:53.980
Want me to work overtime for you?

39:55.160 --> 39:55.880
Yiming,

39:55.920 --> 39:57.500
it takes a while to heal.

39:57.530 --> 39:58.770
You need to rest.

39:58.900 --> 40:00.280
Don't leave behind any lasting health issues.

40:07.140 --> 40:07.970
Let me tell you.

40:08.010 --> 40:09.770
He's held back for days.

40:09.800 --> 40:10.960
He wanted to get discharged two days ago,

40:10.980 --> 40:12.090
but we pressed him down.

40:12.110 --> 40:13.870
For us police,

40:13.900 --> 40:15.160
a leg is nothing.

40:15.620 --> 40:16.590
It's nothing.

40:16.610 --> 40:17.130
Stand properly.

40:17.160 --> 40:18.090
I have something to tell you.

40:18.120 --> 40:19.410
-Come.
-Attention!

40:19.780 --> 40:21.130
Captain Jiang said

40:21.170 --> 40:23.190
next weekend,

40:23.210 --> 40:24.680
if you all don't have cases

40:24.700 --> 40:26.300
and aren't working overtime,

40:26.470 --> 40:28.340
he'll ask Dr. Lu's coworkers to eat

40:28.370 --> 40:29.420
roast lamb with us.

40:30.270 --> 40:31.370
Roast lamb?

40:31.480 --> 40:32.860
[Collective Third-Class Merit]

40:33.390 --> 40:35.190
Keep your voices down. It's work hours. Stop it.

40:35.190 --> 40:36.210
Thank you, Captain Jiang.

40:36.430 --> 40:37.310
It’s just a possibility, okay?

40:37.330 --> 40:38.250
Get to work.

40:39.830 --> 40:40.590
Are you ignoring me?

40:40.610 --> 40:41.650
You're ignoring me?

40:41.700 --> 40:44.560
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

41:14.640 --> 41:15.110
Yes.

41:17.380 --> 41:18.150
Okay.

41:26.170 --> 41:27.060
There was a car accident.

41:27.080 --> 41:27.890
Dr. Lu,

41:27.910 --> 41:28.940
come quickly.

41:29.560 --> 41:30.580
The patient's blood pressure is unstable.

41:35.030 --> 41:36.070
What's going on?

41:36.250 --> 41:37.740
The patient’s arteries were not affected.

41:38.010 --> 41:39.610
Okay, I'll arrange the surgery right away.
